Email
    email Text
    userId UserId Maybe
    verkey Text Maybe
    UniqueEmail email
Comment json -- Adding "json" causes ToJSON and FromJSON instances to be derived.
    message Text
    userId UserId Maybe
    deriving Eq
Entry
   user UserId
   entry EntryId
   title Text
   posted UTCTime
   content Textarea 


